## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available literature up to October 2023. The rapidly evolving nature of climate science means that new findings could alter current understandings. Additionally, the complexity of ecological interactions and the variability of climate impacts across different regions and species may not be fully captured in the existing studies. Further research is needed to continuously update and refine these findings.